title: How to Launch a Life Coaching Career
headline: Discover the coaching methods, tools and business skills you need to excel as a life coach in this free online course.
description: Are you a ‘people person’ who wants to help others attain their goals? This skill-building life coaching course explores the ‘I-CAN-DO’ coaching model, representational systems, fundamental rapport skills and other coaching tools. In addition, we will discuss business guidelines to show you how to get your first client and grow your practice. This course will enrich you with the knowledge you need to succeed in your career as a life coach.
courseDescription:
Since the 1990s, life coaching has grown in popularity as people at different stages in life desire and seek success in their finances, relationships, careers and health. A medical professional and a life coach, Amer Taha, has helped many students reach their goals and objectives through his courses. But what is ‘life coaching’? Is it the same as therapy or counselling? You might be surprised by what you'll discover.

The first topic lays a solid foundation for understanding life coaching by defining and explaining it. Next, we go through the basics of what it entails, focusing on fundamental coaching beliefs and the essential communication skills you will need as you work with your clients. We will discuss how to build your coaching practice in-depth, precisely where to begin and how to grow it. We explore how to coach to gain results. You will learn the concepts of ‘framing’, ‘reframing’, ‘matters of state’ and representational systems - all of which are necessary for effective life coaching.

The final sections examine meta language patterns and the ‘spiral’ coaching model. Delve into the secrets of coaching success and review the guidelines for specialisation in your coaching practice. Whether you are looking to change careers or just about to launch one, this course will benefit you if you are passionate about helping others reach their full potential. We will equip you with the professional skills and tools required to chart a clear path and establish a successful life coaching business. Enrol today!

  • Lesson Summary - Life Coaching Workshop

  • Life coaching though not an entirely new practice is gaining more and more popularity as more people seek to succeed in their personal and professional lives. Life coaching is a career and an ethical profession. The life coach uses the power of commitment to enable their clients to achieve beneficial and measurable results in all areas of their lives.

  • Select an Image from the Gallery

  • Life coaching is a holistic process that has the power to balance and harmonize life. It concentrates on the person’s whole life instead of just one area. It is absolutely nothing about giving advice or imposing knowledge on your clients.

  • Select an Image from the Gallery

  • Life coaching removes the interference that stands between clients and the achievement of their potential. Concentrate on balancing all the areas of your client's life.
    Believe that your clients have all the resources they need to solve their own problems and that it is your job to help them remove the obstacles that prevent this from happening.
    You can develop your techniques, your own style and proficiency to become a highly sought-after life coach.
